| Detail | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Chain** | Arbitrum (chainId: `42161`) |
| **Amount** | `0.1 ETH` → `parseEther("0.1")` |
| **Recipient** | `0x742d35Cc...` |
| **Method** | ERC-4337 User Operation |

### ⚠️ Important Considerations

1. **Gas funding** — Your smart account needs ETH to pay for gas. Either:
   - Fund the smart account address directly with ETH, **or**
   - Add a paymaster for sponsored/gasless transactions

2. **First-time deployment** — If this is a new smart account, the first user operation will also deploy the contract (handled automatically via `initCode`).

3. **Bundler URL** — Replace the Pimlico URL with your preferred bundler. Other options:
   - [Alchemy](https://www.alchemy.com/account-abstraction)
   - [Stackup](https://www.stackup.sh/)
