  client: publicClient,
  transport: http("https://public.pimlico.io/v2/42161/rpc"),
  paymaster: paymasterClient, // Sponsor gas fees
});
```

This sends the ETH transfer as a **User Operation** through the ERC-4337 flow, giving you smart account benefits like batching, gas abstraction, and delegation support.

